, define 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lebInt{\mu}f:=\sup\left\{ \bar{\mu}_{0}\left(s\right)\mid s\in\mathcal{M}_{\textnormal{sim}}\left(\X,\F\right)\textnormal{ such that }s\leq f\right\} .
\]

