\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "cor:changeOfVariables"

\end_inset

Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\X,\F,\mu\right)$
\end_inset

 be a measure space and define 
\begin_inset Formula $f\mu$
\end_inset

 to be the image measure of a function 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\nonnegMeasurableFunctions$
\end_inset

 with respect to measure 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu.$
\end_inset

