\begin_layout Proposition
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "prop:intZeroFuncZero"

\end_inset

For any function 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\nonnegMeasurableFunctions$
\end_inset

 and a measure 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $\F$
\end_inset

, if the integral 
\begin_inset Formula $\lebInt{\mu}f=0$
\end_inset

