Sometimes, this is denoted even more compactly as 
\begin_inset Formula $f\stackrel{\textnormal{a.e}}{=}g.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

 From this it's clear that the set 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ x\in\X\mid f\left(x\right)\neq g\left(x\right)\right\} \subseteq A.$
